data.description: ***** Price Refresher******GREAT PORTFOLIO LISTING! Great opportunity to own a charming 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom townhouse in Calloway Crossing with no rental restrictions and low HOA fees.Main floor of this home offers a large Living Room/Dining Room Combination with a ton of natural light from the bay window. A huge kitchen with a laundry room. Half bath and a giant Storage closet.  Upstairs there you will see the Large Primary bedroom with a large Walk in closet. The Primary Bedroom leads to the Primary bathroom with a two sink, separate tub and shower. There are also two other oversized secondary bedrooms. Townhome includes two dedicated parking spots on the back side of the townhouse with access through he kitchen to the home.  This property offers convenient access to local amenities, schools, shopping, and dining options. Commuting is made easy with nearby, highways and transportation routes. Great property for a first time home buyer or an investor looking for great rental income.
